Types of statistics: 1.Descriptive statistics 2. Inferential statistics

Descriptive statistics: summarize the sample

Measures that used to describe the data:
1.The Measures of central tendency 
  Arithmetic Mean = sum of value in the dataset/No.of values in the dataset
  If Evenly spaced Numbers [3,6,9,12] then
     Arithmetic Mean = Median = (First Term + Last Term) / 2
  Python: import statistics,statistics.mean
    

